OL,3,CResponse stood down after report of
OL,4,Cpossible armed person at primary school
OL,6,FThere is "no risk to pupils, staff or
OL,7,Fthe wider community" after a report of
OL,8,Fa person with a potential weapon at a
OL,9,FJersey primary school, the island's
OL,10,Fpolice force has confirmed.
OL,12,FFirearms officers were sent to
OL,13,FGrouville School at around 11:30am on
OL,14,FThursday.
OL,16,FOne parent has told ITV News that
OL,17,Ftheir child was kept in their
OL,18,Fclassroom with the blinds down and was
OL,19,Fnot allowed to leave to go to the
OL,20,Ftoilet.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
