FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783781277
OL,3,CResponse stood down after report of
OL,4,Cpossible armed person at primary school
OL,6,FThe States of Jersey Police says: "The
OL,7,Finitial report related to a male in
OL,8,Fthe vicinity of the school who was
OL,9,Fbelieved to be carrying a potential
OL,10,Fweapon.
OL,12,F"Officers attended immediately and,
OL,13,Ffollowing enquiries conducted in
OL,14,Fpartnership with the school and CYPES
OL,15,F(Children, Young People, Education and
OL,16,FSkills Department), established that
OL,17,Fthere was no risk to pupils, staff or
OL,18,Fthe wider community.
OL,26,@wD@ApmxD@Rpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
