OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783781277
OL,3,CResponse stood down after report of
OL,4,Cpossible armed person at primary school
OL,6,F"While this incident was quickly
OL,7,Fresolved, we take all reports of this
OL,8,Fnature seriously and would always
OL,9,Fencourage islanders to contact us if
OL,10,Fthey have concerns or observe anything
OL,11,Fthey believe may pose a risk to public
OL,12,Fsafety."
OL,14,FIn an email to parents seen by ITV
OL,15,FNews, headteacher Nichola Turner says:
OL,16,F"A member of staff reported a
OL,17,Fsuspicious matter outside the school
OL,18,Fgrounds and the police were contacted
OL,19,Fimmediately as a precaution.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
