OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783781277
OL,3,CResponse stood down after report of
OL,4,Cpossible armed person at primary school
OL,6,F"All pupils remained safely inside the
OL,7,Fschool building, where they were
OL,8,Fsupervised by staff at all times.
OL,10,F"We understand that incidents of this
OL,11,Fnature can be unsettling for families.
OL,12,FHowever, I would like to reassure you
OL,13,Fthat the school responded
OL,14,Fappropriately and in line with agreed
OL,15,Fsafety and safeguarding procedures."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
